This is a web based Weather application created using Raspberry Pi B+
The app uses DHT 22 sensor for getting temperature and humudity readings
One can use this app  primarily for:
   - real time monitoring of tmp. and humidity data
   - historical weather data analysis

technologies used on the pi:
minibian,python, nginx, uwsgi, flask, jinja, sqlite3, plotly, arrow, js, css, html
